[Route53 Summary]

DNS Exam tips!

- load balancer cannot have IPv4 address, only DNS name
- understand difference between alias record and CNAME
- given the choice, always choose alias record over CNAME

= Routing Policies =

1. Simple Routing policy
	- nothing special, just goes to where it is
	- stupid round robin

2. Weighted
	- A/B testing, 80% 20% etc
 
3. Latency
	- based on latency to end user
	- get quickest performance

4. Failover
	- backup site only comes online when primary fails health check

5. Geolocation
	- based on where the users are geographically located